description: You stand just outside the entrance of a hobbit hole.
You are in the entrance hallway of the hobbit hole. A wizened wizard and small hobbit stand nearby looking curiously at you.
You are at a crossroad. Which direction will you go?
Little hobbits wonder what a tall stranger is doing in their hole. They don't know where you're going.
Oh no! Dead end! You must have taken a wrong turn somewhere.
Hobbit merriment is underway! You join in for a short while… but then it is time to continue to seek the lost treasure.
TREASURE FOUND! aka YOU GOT THE JOB!!!!! Woooo! Thank you for playing :)
